### Media Queries

**Media queries** apply CSS based on device characteristics (screen size, orientation, etc.).

---

### Syntax

```css
@media media-type and (condition) {
  /* CSS rules */
}
```

---

### Media Types

```css
@media screen { /* For screens (default) */ }
@media print { /* For printers */ }
@media all { /* All devices */ }
@media speech { /* Screen readers */ }
```

---

### Common Breakpoints

```css
/* Mobile-first approach */

/* Default styles (mobile) */

/* Tablet */
@media (min-width: 768px) { }

/* Desktop */
@media (min-width: 1024px) { }

/* Large desktop */
@media (min-width: 1280px) { }
```

---

### Logical Operators

```css
/* AND */
@media (min-width: 600px) and (max-width: 1024px) { }

/* OR (comma separated) */
@media (max-width: 600px), (orientation: landscape) { }

/* NOT */
@media not print { }

/* Only (for older browsers) */
@media only screen and (min-width: 768px) { }
```

---

### Media Features

| Feature | Example |
|---------|---------|
| `width` | `(min-width: 768px)` |
| `height` | `(max-height: 600px)` |
| `orientation` | `(orientation: portrait)` |
| `aspect-ratio` | `(aspect-ratio: 16/9)` |
| `resolution` | `(min-resolution: 2dppx)` |
| `hover` | `(hover: hover)` |
| `prefers-color-scheme` | `(prefers-color-scheme: dark)` |
| `prefers-reduced-motion` | `(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)` |

---

### Dark Mode

```css
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  body {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #f0f0f0;
  }
}
```

---

### Print Styles

```css
@media print {
  nav, footer { display: none; }
  body { font-size: 12pt; }
  a[href]::after { content: " (" attr(href) ")"; }
}
```

> **Best Practice:** Use **mobile-first** (`min-width`) queries for cleaner, simpler CSS.
